body.description: The Bush Business Furniture Universal Garage Storage Cabinet with Doors and Shelves features a commercial quality design that's built to last and provides ample room for organization. Neatly store tools, supplies and miscellaneous household items inside a practical garage cabinet that promises to maintain its contemporary style throughout years of reliable use. Cabinet doors with smooth Euro-style hinges open to reveal one fixed shelf and one adjustable shelf that accommodate items of various sizes. Each shelf supports up to 50 pounds, so storing larger materials is no problem. The freestanding floor cabinet's base includes adjustable levelers to compensate for uneven surfaces and wall attachment hardware is included for family-friendly safety and stability. Contemporary finish options include Storm Gray, Platinum Gray and White, all complemented by Brushed Nickel hardware. This 2 door storage cabinet has been meticulously tested to meet or exceed ANSI/BIFMA quality standards for safety and performance and is backed by the Bush Business Furniture 10 Year Manufacturer's Warranty. Create your own modular storage solution by adding the Universal Garage Storage Cabinet with Drawer and Shelves, Garage Storage Cabinet with Drawers, Garage Wall Cabinet with Doors, Narrow Garage Storage Cabinet and Tall Garage Storage Cabinet with Doors (coordinating items sold separately).
